Class AuthToken

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.server.commonClasses.modelClasses.AuthToken

  • public class AuthToken
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Cory on 2/17/17. The AuthToken class specifies a token a user will utilize to log in and authenticate to our main.server.
